    "Thus, each sentence pair's calculated result is utilized only once for the computation of Pcc or MSE.",
    "Results and Discussion Comparing with Other MethodsIn this section, the parameters are set as follows.",
    "Tlarge: uncased (whole word masking), Layer = 24, hidden = 1024, heads = 16 and 340M parameters.",
